{"tid":924789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】拖至2020年先反枱","createTime":"2018-12-02T11:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T16:28:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d5069b35216e406d547150b7789201ea0175614a","tid":924789,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:17:35.000Z","msg":"習特會和好結束，情況與我日前估計的「最好」的情況一樣，即原有的關稅不會取消，但是暫時停止加徵關稅，一切保持原狀90日，讓雙方進一步商談中國該如何開放市場。<br />\n<br />\n目前美國向年值2,000億美元的中國產品徵收10%，另外向年值600億美元的中國產品徵收25%關稅。此外，還有約年值2,500億美元中國產品，包括iPhone並沒有特別加徵關稅，如此做法實際上對中國仍然有利，因為人民幣兌美元已經貶值10%，對沖了年值2,000億美元的10%關稅，相信未來90日，中美貿易順差依然會增加。<br />\n<br />\n之前我也分析過，加徵25%關稅對中國不利，對特朗普也不利，這是習特會成功的理由。實際上，習特會與數個月前特金會沒多大分別，特朗普與金正恩會面後，特朗普並沒有取消對北韓的制裁，北韓也沒有銷毀任何核彈、飛彈，一切依舊，只是少了一些彼此挑戰的行動，即北韓不搞核彈試炸、不射飛彈，美國暫停、縮小美國與南韓的軍事演習。<br />\n<br />\n我認為，特朗普所作所為，目的只是為了2020年的總統選舉，因此，過早成功逼北韓銷毀核彈、飛彈，到了2020年，美國選民就忘記了特朗普今日的功勞。同樣的，如果中國過早開放市場，美國選民在2020年也會忘記今日特朗普的功謀。正如1991年，剛剛逝世的老布殊總統，成功地打敗伊拉克時，聲望如日中天，民調支持度超過80%，為歷任總統之冠，但是，僅僅一年之後，即1992年，老布殊無法連任，敗給克林頓，美國選民忘了1991年老布殊的功勞。<br />\n<br />\n因此，中美貿易戰，特朗普與習近平都在拖，拖至2020年，中國才真正讓步或反枱。<br />\n<br />\n曾淵滄<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181202&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58984203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181202%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58984203&d=jWUPf6E296uzEMOVpP4tvO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=22e0f8ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181202%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58984203&h=1f98e150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181202&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58984203</a>"},{"pid":"6bf628e696906cfaf282948defa45621e9bdee4c","tid":924789,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aada50b7013b238860a71a5a5ca0934648d0280","tid":924789,"uid":71770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"逃生門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0e3cb514f1353c2df8f3035d40ca1d506eeb0c","tid":924789,"uid":190431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:20:10.000Z","msg":"大陸賭侵侵連任唔到，2021又開始選過"},{"pid":"2862475ef966233b098525b95782238e1a3b9383","tid":924789,"uid":26329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"de0e3cb514f1353c2df8f3035d40ca1d506eeb0c","tid":924789,"uid":190431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:20:10.000Z","msg":"大陸賭侵侵連任唔到，2021又開始選過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:36:21.000Z","msg":"間接幫左侵侵 因為問題未解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f8a73b7c7d82daf08c29d2dac43f9f26d516fb","tid":924789,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7127fca6bbde3c882cfc37841defe59ecfbdec11","tid":924789,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e1dc0c75ec1df55c3c34efcf87a410cf53f808","tid":924789,"uid":142233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T15:03:45.000Z","msg":"美國選民諗野咁有趣既"},{"pid":"c96c691155be2d06118097d2418204bc89851463","tid":924789,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"笑到噴飯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e385711383f8364fa66023f501e98c1c5459958","tid":924789,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-